      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>Three fragments, not joining, from an <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">architrave</rs> with decoration (which is broken away) above three stepped <term>fasciae</term>, diminishing in height; a and c: not measured; b: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.52</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.37</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.54</measure>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the upper two <term>fasciae</term>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>Upper <term>fascia</term> <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.10</measure>, lower <term>fascia</term> <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.08</measure>; elongated, ornate.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date notAfter="0500" exact="none" precision="circa" notBefore="0468">Late fifth century</date> (<rs type="criteria">prosopography</rs>)</p>
      </div>

      <div n="text" lang="grc" type="edition">
        <head lang="en">Edition</head>
		<div type="textpart_fragment" n="a"><ab>
		<lb n="1"/><gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> <w lemma="παστάς">παστάδα</w> <w lemma="κίων">κίον'</w> <w lemma="ἐκ">ἐκ</w> <orig n="unresolved"><unclear reason="damage">ιι</unclear></orig><gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>
		<lb n="2"/><gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><orig n="unresolved"><unclear reason="damage">τ</unclear></orig> <persName key="Pytheas" type="aphrodisian" full="yes"><name reg="Πυθέας">Πυθέας</name></persName> <orig n="unresolved"><unclear reason="damage">ορσιιιυ</unclear></orig><gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>
		</ab></div><div type="textpart_fragment" n="b"><ab><lb n="1"/><gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> <w lemma="κάμνω">καμνοῦσαν</w> <w lemma="ἀνάγκη">ἀνάγκῃ</w> <orig n="unresolved"><unclear reason="damage">κ</unclear></orig><gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>
		<lb n="2"/><gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><orig n="unresolved"><unclear reason="damage">ι</unclear></orig> <w lemma="ἔχω">ἔσχε</w> <w lemma="νόος">νόον</w> <space dim="horizontal"/> <gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>
		</ab></div><div type="textpart_fragment" n="c"><ab><lb n="1"/><gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><orig n="unresolved"><unclear reason="damage">α</unclear></orig><gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>
		<lb n="2"/><gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/><orig n="unresolved">δι<unclear reason="damage">ι</unclear></orig><gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>
		</ab></div>
      </div>

      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <p>
		a. <gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">built the</supplied> colonnade <supplied reason="subaudible">with</supplied> column from <gap dim="internal" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/> Pytheas <gap dim="right" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/></p><p>b. <gap dim="left" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/>suffering from necessity <gap dim="internal" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/> had a mind.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head>
        <p>For Pytheas see <xref type="inscription" n="55" href="110070">11.70</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="56" href="020020">2.20</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="57" href="080610">8.610</xref>, <xref type="inscription" n="250" href="150361">15.361</xref> and discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="V.18">V.18</xref>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="history" n="locations"><head>Locations</head><p><rs type="found"><rs key="HadrBath" type="monuList">Hadrianic Baths, East Court</rs>: a: '<foreign lang="fr">Dans le 2e entrée à partir du S<supplied reason="abbreviation">ud</supplied> du portique O<supplied reason="abbreviation">uest</supplied>, s<supplied reason="abbreviation">ud</supplied></foreign>' (Boulanger); b: '<foreign lang="fr">Term. S<supplied reason="abbreviation">ud</supplied> du portique O<supplied reason="abbreviation">uest</supplied></foreign>'. (Boulanger).</rs>. Original location: <rs type="origLocation">Unknown.</rs>. <rs type="lastLocation">Among the material from the French excavations in the East Court.</rs>. </p></div>

      

      

      <div type="history" n="record">
        <head>History of Recording</head>
        <p>a and b excavated by <rs type="visitor" key="boulanger">Boulanger</rs>, <date value="1913" notBefore="1913" notAfter="1913" exact="both">1 November 1913</date> (notebook A, 78, 23 and 24, whence B 23, 29); a, b and c recorded by the NYU expedition, c in <date value="1989" notBefore="1989" notAfter="1989" exact="both">1989</date>.</p>
      </div>

